{"tid":2510724,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［突發］兩男女被捕 28歲男涉煽動分裂國家藏械等3罪","createTime":"2021-04-30T10:54:56.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-30T11:19:33.000Z","uid":204226,"like":20,"dislike":75,"uniUserReply":92,"replies":[{"pid":"dbb28754b3221dc716578c010693d33a4c9a57f1","tid":2510724,"uid":204226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T10:54:56.000Z","msg":"港版國安法｜兩男女被捕 28歲男涉煽動分裂國家藏械等3罪<br />\n<br />\n【蘋果日報】警方表示，國家安全處經調查後，今日於長沙灣拘捕一名28歲男子，涉嫌「煽動分裂國家」、「無牌經營槍械」及「藏有攻擊性武器」等；以及在將軍澳拘捕一名22歲女子，涉嫌「無牌經營槍械」。被捕男女現正被扣留調查。（原文）<br />\n<br />\n#20210430新聞<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210430/GB42KI7JMFAX5LYSIDSSKKWZHI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210430%2FGB42KI7JMFAX5LYSIDSSKKWZHI%2F&d=SQXEpmicj55cx%2FeODTqnT1QYB6qXEwX4CB7r1YlVkGU%3D&h=bdb28c69\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210430%2FGB42KI7JMFAX5LYSIDSSKKWZHI%2F&h=2f9d322b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210430/GB42KI7JMFAX5LYSIDSSKKWZHI/</a>"},{"pid":"b9c871327fabdadb6c8e263b4ab525630f8ee573","tid":2510724,"uid":204226,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T10:55:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb7a08039ee338be14f6c8e017cacf69f6982dcf","tid":2510724,"uid":204226,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T10:55:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c08d273bc9fb00565be46359dcdef15f8c032ab2","tid":2510724,"uid":3229